channel.title: Signing into my default gateway?
channel.description: When i copy my default gateway and put it into my firefox address bar it takes me to my internet provider, verizon. however how do i log in on that page? my normal verizon account won't work... some people just told me to put "admin" as the username but that doesn't work either... any solutions?
